message.content:
The environment is a kitchen and dining room. The kitchen has a dark gray cabinet with a beige countertop. On the countertop are a stack of white plates, a jar of jam, a box of strawberry banana Jello, and a package of Alpen Salt. To the right of the counter is a sink, a pot on a stove, and various food items. Above the counter are more dark gray cabinets. There is a white refrigerator to the right of the counter. 

The dining room has a wooden table with four white chairs. On the table are a bottle of Evian water, a book titled "Chocolate Cake Killers", and a plate with a bowl and other items. 

The floors are made of wood in a herringbone pattern. The walls are white. There is a door in the dining room. A round light fixture hangs from the ceiling in the dining room.
